GIS

Class MetaDataElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • GIS.MetaDataElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Meta_data

    public class MetaDataElement
extends java.lang.Object
implements Meta_data
    This class represent the data on every point in the kml. Data such as : UTC(time and date) , name , _AccuracyMeters , type , color and more . the time in data displayed in two ways, as string and long. longToString function allows us to convert time shown as long back to string. * @author DanielAbergel
